HOSTING README

Requirements (hosting):
    1. Linux
    2. Python 3.4+
    3. PyCrypto library

Notes for the host:
    - options of the challenge can be modified in constants.py
    - start the server using python3 main.py
    - allow the listen port in the firewall
    - message lengths of 16, 24 or 32 bytes are permitted only
    - CTRL + C will terminate the program
    
Tested on python 3.4, 3.5

